{"tid":2167171,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"\"被中國國籍法\" 原來係源於 大清國籍條例","createTime":"2020-08-21T02:19:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T04:25:47.000Z","uid":14918,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"db724a72cdc4d8f0bbe4eebb7c0b70448726a6db","tid":2167171,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:19:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%85%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25B1%258D%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliux6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=9dd0f7e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%A4%A7%E6%B8%85%E5%9C%8B%E7%B1%8D%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B</a><br />\n第一條<br />\n凡左列人等<span class=\"red\">不論是否生於中國地方均屬中國國籍</span>︰<br />\n一) 生而父為中國人者<br />\n二) 生於父死後而父死時為中國人者<br />\n三) 母為中國人而父無可考或無國籍者。<br />\n<br />\n第二條<br />\n若父母均無可考或均無國籍而生於中國地方者亦屬中國國籍。其生地並無可考而在中國地方發現之棄童同。<br />\n<br />\n血源詛咒, 而家支共翻炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9GQ7Yg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9GQ7Yg.jpg&h=4c067b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新國籍法:中國國籍永遠有效<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035816\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035816</a>"},{"pid":"f58f60767f79041f51879072c365dd12bc0e9b14","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"基本法都抄左<br />\n其實咩叫中國人非常含糊<br />\n粵客閩係百越唔係漢人"},{"pid":"b90247035b37eca399ced08fac667825041ca54f","tid":2167171,"uid":73598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"大清叫自已中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1aba9857d411e3e9fb2dcac275b552a7422c62f","tid":2167171,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"咁係咪要還債？"},{"pid":"3ce2cb7a9b1ff8137842ba3ba7ff9a0e7abd4d67","tid":2167171,"uid":53766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"簡單d講<br />\n1. 拎到外國籍都記得一定要取消中國籍<br />\n2. 想生仔既記得雙方都取消中國籍，唔係就累死後代"},{"pid":"f70c54295c1b085056d215c09385826676878cc4","tid":2167171,"uid":271545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b90247035b37eca399ced08fac667825041ca54f","tid":2167171,"uid":73598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"大清叫自已中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:42:00.000Z","msg":"自入主中原之後，清朝皇帝正式以「中國」（滿語：ᡩᡠᠯᡳᠮᠪᠠᡳ<br />\nᡤᡠᡵᡠᠨ，轉寫：dulimbai gurun）稱呼全境[參 35][參 36]。1689年，清朝康熙帝在與俄國簽訂的具有現代國際法水準的邊界條約&mdash;&mdash;《尼布楚條約》中，首次將「中國」作為正式國家名稱使用，與「俄羅斯」相對[註 9][參 37]，該「中國」指包括蒙古以及中國東北等地在內的整個清帝國[參 38]。<br />\nfrom wiki"},{"pid":"dd23ef6955ec1b672f325d486d1b95085b54a870","tid":2167171,"uid":44674,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b90247035b37eca399ced08fac667825041ca54f","tid":2167171,"uid":73598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T02:58:08.000Z","msg":"大清叫自已中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"根據中共史觀，忽必烈都叫自己中國人"},{"pid":"27c3d3a3de695b2a2d22beb96b5eb5d2d08bf9ac","tid":2167171,"uid":106641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3ce2cb7a9b1ff8137842ba3ba7ff9a0e7abd4d67","tid":2167171,"uid":53766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:37:12.000Z","msg":"簡單d講<br />\n1. 拎到外國籍都記得一定要取消中國籍<br />\n2. 想生仔既記得雙方都取消中國籍，唔係就累死後代"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:52:58.000Z","msg":"中共：你可以申請取消，但我們唔承認你個取消申請"},{"pid":"88ba1cd3ff11446eaf926089effc676ad65e399f","tid":2167171,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"咁就要孭埋清朝條數"},{"pid":"dc5f3cd9d66e9eed91fcd8068a58cba941d7bd5b","tid":2167171,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88ba1cd3ff11446eaf926089effc676ad65e399f","tid":2167171,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"咁就要孭埋清朝條數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:06:01.000Z","msg":"呢啲時候佢哋就會承認中華民國"},{"pid":"0f87b39a0576c2bd20c38c60148f4d4e56a69aaf","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:16:02.000Z","msg":"吞西藏時就話藏族都係中國人<br />\n但香港印巴其實都可以聲稱係藏人<br />\n理應全香港印巴都自動成為中國人"},{"pid":"ba22f20b8c3e8fdf0eb55bdb1fa6e4d9d17f8731","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"所以中國人定義係龍門任搬"},{"pid":"f1187ce2e8ecc6c02ceba2a5536047181b91aa66","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"支持香港出世印巴全部聲稱自己國籍係中國西藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58be4972d26964e6d4922772721eeb639f776bba","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"支持所以香港出世中東人自稱國籍係中國新疆<br />\n印巴國籍係中國西藏<br />\n白種人自稱中國俄羅斯族<br />\n全部自動入籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd03831ca7742df949c35162e113aea03ceee64","tid":2167171,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1187ce2e8ecc6c02ceba2a5536047181b91aa66","tid":2167171,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"支持香港出世印巴全部聲稱自己國籍係中國西藏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"印度支那省"},{"pid":"eb5fc889c1338f167bb49e650e6ad95b7bb09514","tid":2167171,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec5213848231cc6c7eb60f2f8a733607259d8